            "text_PcTJVF": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>How can we restore our relationship with the soil, so that we both may flourish?</p><p>We believe the answer lies in reverence, in rhythm, in the quiet understanding that we are not separate from nature but a part of it. To take without giving, to rush without listening, only breaks the delicate balance that has sustained life for centuries. Instead, we choose another way, the Cala Falcó Way. <br/>Here, we move with intention, honouring the soil, the sea, the air we breathe, everything above us, beneath us, and beside us. We craft with care, believing that true luxury is not in abundance but in the rare, the meaningful, the deeply personal. We find a deeper sense of happiness, trusting that time enriches everything it touches. Ingredients, experiences, even ourselves. <br/><br/>And we discover a level of health and wellbeing that isn’t temporary, but transformative. For the mind, body, and spirit. We have been conditioned to accept the artificial as normal. But deep down, we long for something real. Something regenerative. A life woven with the elements, not against them. <br/>At Cala Falcó, we listen to nature as a teacher, a guide, a partner. And we bring our teachings into today, modernising ancient values for a new era. This is more than a philosophy. It is an invitation.To return to something pure, joyful, and enduring.<br/><br/>Welcome to our way. The Cala Falcó way.</p>",
                "width": "100%",
                "max_width": "none",
                "alignment": "left",
                "type_preset": "rte",
                "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
